t;  Lyrick gets up out of the bed, half dressed in his evening wear.  &quot;I need to get dressed and make sure I'm packed.  Thank you kindly, Vaelara.  You have been most hospitable.&quot;  He bows in thanks and drops about 5 gold in the teacup she was holding.  &quot;Here.  A donation to your church.&quot;  She smiles at Lyrick, gives him a small kiss on the cheek, and tells him, &quot;Thank you.  I'll try to see you off.&quot;  And with that, Vaelara leaves the cottage.<br>
